ADR 0143 BIDS 1.11.1 first-class coverage fixture.

Carries one scalp recording, one intracranial recording, a gzipped
physiological table, an events table, an electrodes table with a
coordinate system, and one derivative. The EEG, iEEG and derivative EDF
files are deliberately byte-identical: the point of the fixture is that
the same bytes mean different things depending on where BIDS puts them.
